Careers






At Mississippi Power, we strive to deliver world-class value to our customers and communities every day. That's why we look to hire bright, enthusiastic people by offering a stable work environment, a culture that values diversity, inclusion and teamwork and a competitive pay and benefits package. We strongly encourage and support ongoing education and learning, both on and off the job. We offer tuition reimbursement, web-based training and leadership development classes along with competitive pay and outstanding benefits. 
Find current opportunities



College recruiting
Our college recruitment program focuses on opportunities that give you growth and build leadership skills that will last your entire career.
We currently focus on the following areas in our recruitments efforts:

Accounting/Finance
Engineering
Information Technology

Military veterans
At Mississippi Power we offer rewarding careers and challenging opportunities that leverage your discipline, problem-solving skills and leadership abilities.
Professionals & skilled craft
We are always looking for skilled professionals to join our team and we offer packages that are extremely competitive.
Hiring process
Use our online tool to search our openings. If you see an opening that interest you, or you would like to be notified of future opportunities, the first step is to create a candidate profile. 
Please include your work experience, education and skills along with a recent resume for your profile. Once you've created a profile, you can apply online for jobs that match your qualification. You may check your status and update your information at any time.
Sample employment test
Mississippi Power uses pre-employment testing as a way to help identify potential candidates for job openings. We have a variety of tests which include:

Construction and Skill Traded Selection System (CAST)
Customer Service Representative (CSR)
Plant Operator Selection System (POSS)
Power Plant Maintenance Positions Selection System (MASS)
Support and Administrative Selection System (SASS)
Technical Occupations Selection System (TECH)





 




































