Payment Options







Online payment — checking/savings
We now offer the ability to pay your bill online whether you want to login or not. If you login to the site your information will be provided on the page. If you choose to pay without logging in, you will need your account number and your access code from your bill.
Login and Pay Bill —   or   — Pay Bill without Logging In

Credit card payment
Need to pay your bill right away? Now you can by using BillMatrix, an automated payment service.
BillMatrix is a separate company not affiliated with Mississippi Power. BillMatrix will charge you a service fee of $2.25 to handle the payment.
You may submit your payment over the internet or by phone, seven days a week, 24 hours a day. You will need your account number along with a valid credit card, Debit/ATM card or checking account information.
Go to BillMatrix website or call 1-800-834-2073


Auto payment
Auto Pay is a free bill payment program where you can authorize your bill amount to be automatically debited from your checking or savings account. With Auto Pay, we will continue to read your meter and calculate your bill each month. You will continue to receive your bill as you normally do, but instead of "Please Pay By" being displayed on the bill, we will print the date when your bank account will be drafted for the amount of your bill.
Sign up for Auto Pay


Office or authorized payment locations
Find a Mississippi Power office or authorized payment location near you.



U.S. mail
Payment Address:
Mississippi Power Payments
P.O. Box 245
Birmingham, Alabama 35201










Understanding Your Bill
Whether you are looking for your balance and due date, our contact information or available payment options, we are sure you will find our bill format easy to read. Your bill — both electronic and paper — also includes a 13-month graph to track your usage.
View your bill
View paper sample


Sign Up for Paperless Billing
Receive an e-mail notification each month when your paperless bill is sent and get Immediate payment confirmation. No more worrying about your check being lost or arriving late in the mail.
Learn more












 































Mississippi Power Co: Company Profile - Bloomberg



































































  









Feedback















mississippi power co
Public Company









Company Profile
Sector: Utilities
Industry: Utilities
Sub-Industry: Integrated Utilities
Mississippi Power Company provides utility services. The Company generates, transmits, distributes, and sells electricity to residential and commercial uses, as well as offers energy conservation services. Mississippi Power serves customers in the State of Mississippi.




Corporate Information
Address:

PO Box 4079
Gulfport, MS 39502
United States


Phone:
1-800-532-1502


Fax:
-


Web url:
www.mississippipower.com





