                                            Mississippi Power Co is located at Gulfport, MS, and it's an electric services company. It brings in a revenue of $560.7 million annually and employs 1,257 people. A uniquely appealing company, Mississippi Power Co has become quite noticeable in the market. Anthony J Topazi is the firm's CEO.
                                        









