Kemper County
				Energy Facility















Powering Today
Has plant operations about four times better than the industry average.
Find Out More





21st Century Technology
Integrated gasification combined cycle (IGCC) design called TRIGTM. IGCC converts lignite coal to synthesis gas.
Find Out More





Fuel Diversity
Learn about Mississippi lignite and how we are diversifying our fuel portfolio by adding it to our current mix of natural gas and coal.
Find Out More





Environmental Benefits
Preserving our environment through reduced emissions, carbon capture, and being water conscientious.
Find Out More





Economic Benefits
How the Kemper County energy facility is already creating thousands of jobs.
Find Out More





Facts
Find a project overview, facts and figures, the project timeline, and more.
Find Out More





In the Community
As part of our commitment to Kemper County, Mississippi Power has been heavily involved in the community.
Find Out More






 




































